---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="JamJet — Investors"
  description="JamJet is the Agent Action Control layer for production AI agents. Brief deck available on request."
  canonical="https://jamjet.dev/investors"
>

<section class="zn-cover" style="padding: 4rem 0;">
  <div class="zn-shell">

    <div class="zn-masthead">
      <span class="zn-vol">JamJet · Investors</span>
      <span class="zn-issue">Brief deck on request</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="zn-display" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      Investor brief.
    </h1>

    <p class="zn-lede">
      JamJet is the <strong>Agent Action Control</strong> layer for production AI agents. We author the open <a href="https://agentboundary.jamjet.dev/spec/v0.1">AgentBoundary spec</a> + conformance suite that grades every major agent governance vendor (Microsoft AGT, LangSmith Fleet, Cloudflare Agents, Anthropic permission policies), and we monetize through hosted Cloud compliance bundles for regulated mid-market teams.
    </p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 3rem;">What we&rsquo;ve shipped</h2>

    <ul class="zn-list">
      <li><strong>Open-source distribution</strong> on PyPI (<code>jamjet</code>, <code>jamjet-engram</code>), npm (<code>@jamjet/cloud</code> family), Maven Central (<code>dev.jamjet:*</code> across 8 modules), crates.io, GHCR, and the Official MCP Registry.</li>
      <li><strong>JamJet Cloud</strong> live at <a href="https://app.jamjet.dev">app.jamjet.dev</a> — hosted control plane, Stripe-checkout billing, signed audit exports (Ed25519), policy versioning.</li>
      <li><strong>Engram</strong> agent memory product — Python rewrite scoring <strong>88.8% on LongMemEval-S</strong> (proxy benchmark), arXiv paper in preparation. Engram bundled into Cloud.</li>
      <li><strong>JVM-native runtime</strong> (<code>jamjet-runtime-java</code> on Maven Central) — published 8.9× latency speedup vs sidecar pattern, Spring AI + LangChain4j integrations.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 3rem;">Brief deck</h2>

    <p>
      For a current investor brief, including the AgentBoundary spec, JamJet Cloud product, and 12-week operating plan, please email <a href="mailto:investors@jamjet.dev">investors@jamjet.dev</a>.
    </p>

    <p>
      We don&rsquo;t run an active fundraise during the AgentBoundary v0.1 launch window. Inbound interest is welcome; we respond within 5 business days.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.zn-list {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 1.5rem 0;
}
.zn-list li {
  padding: 0.75rem 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--zn-rule, #e5e0d8);
}
.zn-list li:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}
.zn-list code {
  background: var(--zn-code-bg, #f5f1ea);
  padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
  border-radius: 3px;
  font-size: 0.9em;
}
</style>
